---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Door Installation',
  provider: { '@type': 'GeneralContractor', name: 'Purpose Construction', url: 'https://purposeconstructionco.com' },
  areaServed: { '@type': 'State', name: 'Texas', containedIn: { '@type': 'Country', name: 'United States' } },
  description: 'Door installation across East Texas — entry doors, patio doors, French doors, storm doors, and sliding glass doors with weatherstripping, hardware, and trim for East Texas homes.',
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Door Installation East Texas | Purpose Construction"
  description="Door installation across East Texas — entry, patio, French, storm, and sliding glass doors with proper weatherstripping and trim. Purpose Construction serves East Texas homeowners."
  schema={schema}
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Services', href: '/services' }, { label: 'Exterior Services', href: '/exterior-services' }, { label: 'Door Installation', href: '/door-installation' }]} />
  <PageHero title="Door Installation in East Texas" subtitle="Entry doors, patio doors, French doors, and storm doors installed with proper weatherstripping, hardware, and trim — security and efficiency for East Texas homes." tag="Exterior Service" 
    image="/images/door-installation-east-texas.jpg"
  />

  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-50">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <SectionHeading tag="Door Installation" title="Doors That Open, Close, and Seal the Way They Should" />
          <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600">
            <p>A door installation is deceptively technical — a door that isn't perfectly plumb and level won't latch correctly, won't seal against weatherstripping properly, and will develop operational problems within a few months. In East Texas, where homes experience significant humidity fluctuations and wood doors expand and contract seasonally, proper installation technique makes the difference between a door that works well for decades and one that becomes a headache within the first year.</p>
            <p>Purpose Construction installs exterior entry doors, patio doors, French doors, sliding glass doors, and storm doors across East Texas and Angelina County. We handle the complete installation — shimming, fastening, weatherstripping, deadbolt and lockset installation, and exterior and interior trim and casing — so you get a finished product that's weathertight, secure, and good-looking from both sides.</p>
            <p>Storm doors are particularly practical in East Texas for adding a layer of insect protection during spring and fall when the weather is nice enough to leave the main door open. We install quality storm door units that complement your entry door and hold up through years of use.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
            <a href="/exterior-services" class="btn-outline">All Exterior Services</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/images/door-installation-east-texas.jpg" alt="Door installation across East Texas by Purpose Construction" class="rounded-xl shadow-hero" width="640" height="480" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-white border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="What's Included" title="Door Installation Services" align="center" />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
        {['Entry Doors', 'Patio Doors', 'French Doors', 'Storm Doors', 'Sliding Glass Doors', 'Deadbolt & Lockset', 'Weatherstripping', 'Trim & Casing'].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>{item}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding-sm bg-warm-50 border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="Related Services" title="Related Exterior Services" />
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {[{ label: 'Window Installation', href: '/window-installation' }, { label: 'Exterior Painting', href: '/exterior-painting' }, { label: 'Exterior Services', href: '/exterior-services' }].map(link => (
          <a href={link.href} class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700 shadow-card hover:border-brand-red-mid hover:text-charcoal-900 transition-all duration-200">{link.label} →</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-red">
    <div class="container-mid px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="display-md text-white mb-4">Need a New Door Installed?</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-base text-white/80">Contact Purpose Construction for a free door installation estimate. We serve Lufkin and all of East Texas.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost px-8 py-4">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:9365555555" class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150">(936) 555-5555</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
